Package au.edu.federation.caliko

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FabrikBone2D
    A class to represent a FabrikBone2D object.
    FabrikBone3D
    A class to represent a FabrikBone3D object.
    FabrikChain2D
    Class to represent a 2D Inverse Kinematics (IK) chain that can be solved for a given target using the FABRIK algorithm.
    FabrikChain3D
    Class to represent a 3D Inverse Kinematics (IK) chain that can be solved for a given target using the FABRIK algorithm.
    FabrikJoint2D
    Class to represent a joint used to constrain the relative angle between FabrikBone2D objects in an IK chain.
    FabrikJoint3D
    A joint used to constrain the relative angle between FabrikBone3D objects in an IK chain.
    FabrikStructure2D
    A FabrikStructure2D contains one or more FabrikChain2D objects, which we can solve using the FABRIK (Forward And Backward Reaching Inverse Kinematics) algorithm for specified target locations.
    FabrikStructure3D
    A FabrikStructure3D contains one or more FabrikChain3D objects, which we can solve using the FABRIK (Forward And Backward Reaching Inverse Kinematics) algorithm for specified target locations.
